        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And smote of the children of Seir ten thousand — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Who, it appears, were left dead upon the field. How many were only wounded: and not killed, we are not told; but undoubtedly not a few. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Other ten thousand did the children of Judah cast down from the rock — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "A most cruel execution, which can no way be justified, unless the children of Seir had been used to serve in that manner all they took captive of Judah.",
