    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And Amaziah strengthened himself, and led forth his people,.... To go to war with the Edomites; not discouraged by the dismission of the hired troops, but trusting in the promise and power of God, he went forth with boldness and intrepidity: ",
        "children": []
